## Prepare the TinyImageNet Dataset

To utilize our pre-trained models with the TinyImageNet dataset, we developed an index mapping the folder names—each containing class-specific images—to their corresponding WordNet IDs. This index enables users to manually adjust the dataset folder names to match the storage order used in our customized TinyImageNet version, where category folders have been renamed.

Consequently, users can accurately apply the pre-trained models and our code implementation to execute our RDED.
